'''Wild Beasts''' 是一支来自于英格兰肯德尔（Kendal）的[[独立摇滚|独立]]乐队.他们的第一张单曲''Brave Bulging Buoyant Clairvoyants''于2006年11月由Bad Sneakers录制发行,随后他们与[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Domino_Records Domino Records] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Domino_Records |date=20210619180646 }}签约.乐队已经发行了四张广受好评的专辑：2008年发行的''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Limbo,_Panto Limbo, Panto] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Limbo,_Panto |date=20210316142920 }}''、2009年''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Two_Dancers Two Dancers] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Two_Dancers |date=20201112035545 }}'' 、2011年''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Smother_(album) Smother] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Smother_(album) |date=20210316144520 }}''以及2014年的''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Present_Tense_(Wild_Beasts_album) Present Tense] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Present_Tense_(Wild_Beasts_album) |date=20210316154523 }}'' .''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Two_Dancers Two Dancers] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Two_Dancers |date=20201112035545 }}'' 曾获得过英国[[水星音樂獎|水星音乐奖]]提名.

==历史==
2002年,凯瑟琳女王学院的学生Hayden Thorpe和Ben Little组成''“duo Fauve”'',这在法语中的意思为''“Wild Beast”'',并开始创作歌曲.2004年1月,鼓手Chris"Bert"Talbot和贝斯手Gareth"Gaz"Bullock加入乐队,名称改为'''Wild Beasts'''.四人在2004年6月录制了他们的第一张同名demo [[EP|EP]].2005年9月,乐队搬到了[[利兹|利兹]],并且Tom Fleming替代Bullock成为乐队的全职贝斯手.他们在Trash（前身为The Mixing Tin)举行利兹的第一场演出.全新的四人进一步录制了两张demo EP,''Esprit De Corps''以及''All Men''.

Wild Beasts在2006年8月与Bad Sneakers Records签约.他们于2006年11月在[[BBC_6_Music|BBC Radio 6 Music]]的''Marc Riley's Brain Surgery''现场录制了三条音轨<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/6music/shows/brain_surgery/tracklisting_20061222.shtml BBC Tracklisting (Brain Surgery)] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/67Q7ozHY2?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00c72y1 |date=20120504235828 |dateformat=iso }} 2006-12-22</ref>. 随即,Bad Sneakers在11月20号发行了他们的第一张单曲''Brave Bulging Buoyant Clairvoyants''<ref name="Guardian">Simpson, Dave. 2006-12-15 [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] "[http://music.guardian.co.uk/rock/story/0,,1972106,00.html First Sight: Wild Beasts.] {{Wayback|url=http://music.guardian.co.uk/rock/story/0,,1972106,00.html |date=20070322094914 }}"</ref>,伴随主唱Hayden''“大量的假声掩盖了吉他的旋律”（"enormous falsetto voice, which soars over chiming guitars"）''<ref name="Guardian"/>, 这张单曲在英国独立唱片单曲排行榜中获得了第17名的好成绩.

2007年2月,Wild Beasts与Domino Records签约<ref>[[Domino_Records|Domino Records]] 2007-02-22 [http://www.dominorecordco.com/site/index.php?page=news&newsID=603 Domino News] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/67Q7py9my?url=http://www.dominorecordco.com/uk/news/ |date=20120504235842 |dateformat=iso }} Obtained 2007-03-03.</ref>. 同年4月由Bad Sneakers Records发行了第二张单曲''Through Dark Night''<ref>Knight, Beverely. 2007-04-21 [[Music_Week|Music Week]] "The playlist." Page 3.</ref>.5月,Wild Beasts被音乐杂志[[NME|NME]]列为十大“顶尖乐队”之一<ref>Hargreaves, Ellie. 2007-05-23 [[Newsquest|ThisisTheLakeDistrict.co.uk]]. "[http://www.thewestmorlandgazette.co.uk/display.var.1419883.0.0.php NME Hails Kendal Band "Must See"] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/67Q7qpFVb?url=http://www.thewestmorlandgazette.co.uk/leisure/1419883.0/ |date=20120504235855 |dateformat=iso }}" Section: leisure</ref>.Wild Beasts于2008年6月16日发行的首张专辑''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Limbo,_Panto Limbo, Panto] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Limbo,_Panto |date=20210316142920 }}''被描述为''“令人震惊、有趣、重要的是不可改变的”（"shocking, funny, and above all irrevocable"）''<ref>[[Drowned_in_Sound|Drowned in Sound]] [http://drownedinsound.com/articles/3243146 New album: goose-pimpled gods Wild Beasts take debut bow] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/67Q7rcfBt?url=http://drownedinsound.com/news/3243146-new-album--goose-pimpled-gods-wild-beasts-take-debut-bow |date=20120504235907 |dateformat=iso }} Obtained 2008-05-04</ref>.接着,他们又在6月30日发行了单曲''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Devil%27s_Crayon The Devil's Crayon] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Devil%27s_Crayon |date=20171105015009 }}''.

乐队在2009年8月发行了他们的第二张专辑''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Two_Dancers Two Dancers] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Two_Dancers |date=20201112035545 }}'',这张专辑受到了广泛的好评.它被列入了许多2009年精选年度最佳专辑排行名列当中<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/music/reviews/bjhj |title=Wild Beasts Two Dancers Review |access-date=2014-05-02 |archive-date=2021-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316150122/https://www.bbc.co.uk/music/reviews/bjhj/ }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.popmatters.com/pm/review/109159-wild-beasts-two-dancers/ |title=Wild Beasts: Two Dancers |access-date=2014-05-02 |archive-date=2012-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019011329/http://www.popmatters.com/pm/review/109159-wild-beasts-two-dancers/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/music/cd_reviews/article6731988.ece | title=Wild Beasts: Two Dancers|location=London |work=The Times}}</ref>,并被提名为2010年[[水星音樂獎|水星音乐奖]].第三张录音室专辑''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Smother_(album) Smother] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Smother_(album) |date=20210316144520 }}''在2011年5月发行.乐队随即宣布来自''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sky_Larkin Sky Larkin] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sky_Larkin |date=20211121231336 }}''的''Latie Harkin''将加入其成为巡回乐队成员.他们赢得了2011年的''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/London_Awards_for_Art_and_Performance London Awards for Art and Performance] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/London_Awards_for_Art_and_Performance |date=20211121190255 }}''.

乐队在2014年2月24日发行了第四张录音室专辑''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Present_Tense_(Wild_Beasts_album) Present Tense] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Present_Tense_(Wild_Beasts_album) |date=20210316154523 }}''

至今发行的4张专辑都受到了评论家的高度评价.在评论网站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]中,''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Limbo,_Panto Limbo,_Panto] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Limbo,_Panto |date=20210316142920 }}''从17家评论媒体中获得79分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/limbo-panto/wild-beasts |title=Limbo, Panto Reviews - Metacritic |accessdate=2014-01-15 |archive-date=2017-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171106235354/http://www.metacritic.com/music/limbo-panto/wild-beasts }}</ref>（满分100分）,''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Two_Dancers Two_Dancers] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Two_Dancers |date=20201112035545 }}''从19家媒体中获得83分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/two-dancers/wild-beasts |title=Two Dancers Reviews - Metacritic |accessdate=2014-01-15 |archive-date=2021-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423051408/https://www.metacritic.com/music/two-dancers/wild-beasts }}</ref>,''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Smother_(album) Smother] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Smother_(album) |date=20210316144520 }}''从28家媒体中获得85分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/smother/wild-beasts |title=Smother Reviews - Metacritic |accessdate=2014-01-15 |archive-date=2017-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803041304/http://www.metacritic.com/music/smother/wild-beasts }}</ref>,''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Present_Tense_(Wild_Beasts_album) Present Tense] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Present_Tense_(Wild_Beasts_album) |date=20210316154523 }}''从27家媒体中获得86分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/present-tense/wild-beasts |title=Present Tense Reviews - Metacritic |accessdate=2014-03-24 |archive-date=2021-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210809100856/https://www.metacritic.com/music/present-tense/wild-beasts }}</ref>的好成绩.

